flowchart TD
    A[Anchor loss] --> B[Uncertainty diffusion]
    B --> C[Choose small state-informative observation]
    C --> D{Is observation state-informative?}
    D -- no --> E[Not a valid re-anchor]
    D -- yes --> F[Observe result y]
    F --> G[Update belief p(S | y)]
    G --> H{Can next action change?}
    H -- no --> I[Stop observing or act with current plan]
    H -- yes --> J[Choose conditional action a(y)]
    J --> K{Repeat observation useful?}
    K -- yes --> C
    K -- no --> L{Response supports expansion?}
    L -- no --> M[Keep scope small or switch probe]
    L -- yes --> N[Choose expansion factor r_i]
    N --> O[Next scope s_{i+1} = r_i s_i]
    O --> P{Adverse boundary risk acceptable?}
    P -- yes --> Q[Expand scope]
    P -- no --> R[Reduce r_i or observe sooner]
    Q --> C
    R --> C
